text:
This is the first time you and Mano go to the office
together like this. Do you always go from here?
Yeah, I usually take this route.

Oh, I see.
Well, I wish we could see each other more often!
Huh, yeah, that would be nice.

Jeez, Mano, you've been so tense since earlier!
You don't have to be so nervous!

Oops, maybe that was counterproductive...?
But Mano being nervous like that is cute too!

Oh, uh, did I hug you too tightly!?
Are you okay, Mano...?

...Hehe. Yeah, I'm okay.
I was surprised, but I was happy.
